<lb n="0726a07"/><head>No. 786</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0726a08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0726002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【縮】</note><note n="0726002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【縮】<corr resp="say" sic="">＊</corr></note><app n="0726002"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0726003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">木&CB00185;子＝木&CB00185;【三】【縮】＊，木患【宮】＊</note><note n="0726003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">木&CB00185;子＝木&CB00185;【宋】【元】【明】【縮】＊，＝木患【宮】＊</note><app n="0726003"><lem>木&CB00185;<note n="0726004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔子〕－【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726004"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【和】【縮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【縮】" resp="Taisho">木&CB00185;</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">木患</rdg></app>經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0726a09"/>
<lb n="0726a10"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0726005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（失譯…晉錄））八字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯））【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726005" word-count="8"><lem>失譯<note n="0726006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【宋】【元】，人＋（名）【明】</note><app n="0726006"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">人名</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</lem><rdg wit="【和】【縮】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0726a11"/><p><note n="0726007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞如是＝聞如是我聞【和】，如是我聞【縮】</note><note n="0726007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞如是＝聞如是我聞【和】，＝如是我聞【縮】</note><app n="0726007"><lem>聞如是</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">聞如是我聞</rdg><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">如是我聞</rdg></app>。一時佛遊羅閱祇<note n="0726008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闍耆＝闍【和】，嗜闍【縮】</note><note n="0726008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闍耆＝闍【和】，＝嗜闍【縮】</note><app n="0726008"><lem>闍耆</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">闍</rdg><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">嗜闍</rdg></app>崛山中。與
<lb n="0726a12"/>大比丘眾一千二百五十人俱。菩薩無數。名
<lb n="0726a13"/>稱遠聞。<note n="0726009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天人＝人天【縮】</note><app n="0726009"><lem>天人</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">人天</rdg></app>所敬。時難國王。名<note n="0726010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波流離＝波&CB00222;璃【三】【宮】，波琉璃【和】，波&CB00222;璃遣【縮】</note><note n="0726010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波流離＝波&CB00222;璃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝波琉璃【和】，＝波&CB00222;璃遣【縮】</note><app n="0726010"><lem>波流離</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">波&CB00222;璃</rdg><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">波琉璃</rdg><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">波&CB00222;璃遣</rdg></app>。遣
<lb n="0726a14"/>使來到佛所。頂禮佛足。白佛言。世尊。我國
<lb n="0726a15"/>邊<note n="0726011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">小＝少【縮】</note><app n="0726011"><lem>小</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">少</rdg></app>。頻<note n="0726012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歲＝年【縮】</note><app n="0726012"><lem>歲</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">年</rdg></app>寇賊。五穀<note n="0726013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勇＝踴【縮】</note><app n="0726013"><lem>勇</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">踴</rdg></app>貴。<note n="0726014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疾病＝疫疾【三】【宮】，疾疫【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">疾病＝疫疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝疾疫【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726014"><lem>疾病</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">疫疾</rdg><rdg wit="【和】【縮】" resp="Taisho">疾疫</rdg></app>流行。人
<lb n="0726a16"/>民困苦。我&M010527;不得安臥。如來法藏。多悉深廣。
<lb n="0726a17"/>我有<note n="0726015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憂務＝憂勞【宮】</note><app n="0726015"><lem>憂務</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">憂勞</rdg></app>。不得修行。唯願世尊。特垂<note n="0726016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慈愍＝矜愍【三】【宮】【和】，&CB13545;愍【縮】</note><note n="0726016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慈愍＝矜愍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】，＝&CB13545;愍【縮】</note><app n="0726016"><lem>慈愍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】" resp="Taisho">矜愍</rdg><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">&CB13545;愍</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0726a18"/>賜我<note n="0726017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要法＝法要【縮】</note><app n="0726017"><lem>要法</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">法要</rdg></app>。使我日夜易得修行。未來世中。
<lb n="0726a19"/>遠離眾苦</p>
<lb n="0726a20"/><p>佛告王言。若欲滅煩惱障報障者。當貫<note n="0726018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">木&CB00185;＝木患【宮】下同</note><app n="0726018"><lem>木&CB00185;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">木患</rdg></app>
<lb n="0726a21"/>子一<note n="0726019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百＋（一）【三】【宮】【和】【縮】</note><note n="0726019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百＋（一）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726019"><lem>百</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【和】【縮】" resp="Taisho">百一</rdg></app>八。以常自隨。若行若坐若臥。&M010527;<note n="0726020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝常【縮】</note><app n="0726020"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">常</rdg></app>
<lb n="0726a22"/>至心無分散意。稱佛陀<note n="0726021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">達摩＝達磨【三】【宮】【縮】</note><note n="0726021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">達摩＝達磨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】</note><app n="0726021"><lem>達摩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】" resp="Taisho">達磨</rdg></app>僧伽名。乃過一
<lb n="0726a23"/>木&CB00185;子。如是漸次度木&CB00185;子。若十若二十。若
<lb n="0726a24"/>百若千。乃至百千萬。若能滿二十萬遍。身心
<lb n="0726a25"/>不亂。<note n="0726022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無〕－【和】</note><app n="0726022"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>諸諂曲<note n="0726023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【縮】</note><app n="0726023"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。捨<note n="0726024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝身【縮】</note><app n="0726024"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>得生第三焰天。
<lb n="0726a26"/>衣食自然。常安樂行。若復能滿一百萬遍者。
<lb n="0726a27"/>當得斷除百八結業。始名背生死流。趣向泥
<lb n="0726a28"/>洹。永斷煩惱根。獲無上果。<note n="0726025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">信＝使【明】</note><app n="0726025"><lem>信</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>還啟王。王大
<lb n="0726a29"/>歡喜。遙向世尊。頭面禮佛<note n="0726026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝稱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0726026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云＝稱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0726026"><lem>云</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">稱</rdg></app>。大<note n="0726027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＋（哉）【縮】</note><app n="0726027"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">善哉</rdg></app>我當奉
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0786.0726b" n="0726b"/>
<lb n="0726b01"/>行。即&CB00330;吏民。營<note n="0726028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝辨【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726028"><lem>辦</lem><rdg wit="【和】【縮】" resp="Taisho">辨</rdg></app>木&CB00185;子。以為<note n="0726029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">千＝一【宋】【元】</note><app n="0726029"><lem>千</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>具。六親
<lb n="0726b02"/>國戚。皆與一具。王常誦念。雖<note n="0726030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝視【縮】</note><app n="0726030"><lem>親</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">視</rdg></app>軍旅。亦不
<lb n="0726b03"/><note n="0726031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">廢＝癈【縮】</note><app n="0726031"><lem>廢</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">癈</rdg></app>置。又作是念。世尊大慈。普應一切。若我
<lb n="0726b04"/>此<note n="0726032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＋（根）【縮】</note><app n="0726032"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">善根</rdg></app>。得免長<note n="0726033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淪＝沈【縮】</note><app n="0726033"><lem>淪</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">沈</rdg></app>苦海。如來<note n="0726034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＋（身）【和】</note><app n="0726034"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">當身</rdg></app>現。<note n="0726035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【三】【宮】【縮】，〔我身〕－【和】</note><note n="0726035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔我身〕－【和】，〔我〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】</note><app n="0726035"><lem>我身</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【縮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>為
<lb n="0726b05"/><note n="0726036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（我）＋我【和】</note><app n="0726036"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">我我</rdg></app>說法。願樂迫心。<note n="0726037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三日不食＝不食三日【縮】</note><app n="0726037"><lem>三日不食</lem><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">不食三日</rdg></app>。佛即應形。與
<lb n="0726b06"/>諸眷屬。<note n="0726038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來＋（至）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0726038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＋（至）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0726038"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">來至</rdg></app>其宮內。而告王曰。莎<note n="0726039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斗＝升【和】，舛【縮】</note><note n="0726039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斗＝升【和】，＝舛【縮】</note><app n="0726039"><lem>斗</lem><rdg wit="【和】" resp="Taisho">升</rdg><rdg wit="【縮】" resp="Taisho">舛</rdg></app>比丘。誦
<lb n="0726b07"/>三寶名。經歷十歲。得成斯陀含果。漸次習行。
<lb n="0726b08"/>今在普香世界。作辟支佛。王聞是已。倍復修
<lb n="0726b09"/>行。佛告阿難。何況能誦三寶名。經歷<note n="0726040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬數＝萬歲【和】【縮】</note><app n="0726040"><lem>萬數</lem><rdg wit="【和】【縮】" resp="Taisho">萬歲</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0726b10"/>但能聞此人名。生一念隨喜者。未來生處。常
<lb n="0726b11"/>聞十善。說是<note n="0726041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝語【三】【宮】</note><note n="0726041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＝語【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0726041"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">語</rdg></app>時。大眾歡喜。皆願奉行</p>
<lb n="0726b12"/><trailer><title><app type="＊" source="0726002"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【縮】">&lac;</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT17p0726b02"/>木&CB00185;子經</title></trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
